<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, May 4 (Xinhua) -- The International Fund for
Agricultural Development (IFAD) will extend an 8-million-dollar
loan to finance a number of agricultural development projects in
Palestinian self-rule areas.
</P>
<P>
A delegation representing the Rome-based fund is to start
Monday a four-day visit to the Palestinian self-rule areas for
talks with to Palestinian National Authority President Yasser
Arafat and a number of senior officials, the Middle East News
Agency quoted U.N. sources here as saying.
