parliament have taken concerning the 'one China' policy, and their
support for China on the human rights issue," said Li.
</P>
<P>
He noted that the NPC and the Peruvian parliament have
maintained close relations and stressed high-level contacts will
continue to play an important role in promoting the smooth
development of bilateral ties.
</P>
<P>
Li thanked the Peruvian parliamentarians with Chinese ancestry
for their lasting efforts to enhance the China-Peru friendship.
</P>
<P>
He briefed the delegation on the First Session of the Ninth NPC
National Congress, and said the NPC will strengthen its work on
democracy and building a legal system in line with the principle of
governing the country according to law.
</P>
<P>
Rojas pointed to the Chinese ancestry of all people attending
the meeting, and said the delegation is honored to visit the
motherland of their ancestors.
</P>
<P>
He said the Peruvian Congress and the delegates will continue
to contribute to the Peru-China friendship.
</P>
<P>
Li's wife Zhu Lin attended today's meeting along with Zeng
Jianhui, chairman of the NPC Foreign Affairs Committee.
</P>
<P>
The Peruvian delegation is visiting at the invitation of the
NPC Standing Committee. The delegation also met with Tian Jiyun,
vice-chairman of the NPC Standing Committee, and joined in a
Monday working session with Zeng Jianhui. 
