International Arts Festival, a folk craft exhibition opened today
in an arts and crafts complex along bustling Nanjing Road.
</P>
<P>
Folk handcraft has been booming in the Shanghai area for
thousands of years. The exhibition is aimed at exhibiting,
protecting and expanding the crafts which are being challenged by
the modern industry.
</P>
