military envoy that the army of her country has been threatening
the peace process in Bosnia.
</P>
<P>
In a letter to Dzejms Pardj, American military envoy to the
Balkan region, Plavsic demanded that he clarify whether he was
making the statement on behalf of the U.S. government or he was
