proposed a treaty to establish a unified economy in order to
promote the integration process in the CIS.
</P>
<P>
The CIS forum to be held in Moscow next July will discuss
Nazarbayev's other specific proposals on the reforming of CIS
authorities, Tokayen said, adding that the bloc has the potential
to improve its efficiency.
</P>
<P>
The headquarters of the integration committee of the CIS was
moved to Alma Ata in Kazakhstan last week after a decision was
made in the Moscow meeting by the customs union. 
