As for economic cooperation, Insulza said that China is Chile's
second largest trade partner in Asia. Bilateral trade has
constantly increased, while large investments have also been made
between the two countries, he added.
</P>
<P>
"We entrust China with our greatest hope for developing
relations with Asia, and we believe that our trade policy with
China has great dynamism," the minister said. 
