<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON -- The Second meeting between U.S. Secretary of State
Madeleine Albright and Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu
ended Monday evening without any indication that a new Middle East
peace deal is under way.
</P>
<P>
