AMMAN -- King Hussein of Jordan, Saudi Arabian King Fahd Ibn
Abdul Aziz and Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak on Monday
expressed hope that the Palestinian and Israeli leaders will come
out of the London meeting with a breakthrough in the stalled
Mideast peace process.
</P>
<P>
